latestPosts.caption:
Read Caption 🧿✨

[It all started from a random thought, i created my ig becz it was trending back in 2019, when i was in my school days Std. 7th
I still remember meri frnd ne mujhe bola tha ki Instagram pe bade bade log aate hain so that’s why i made my ig too. Idk what’s content creation, influncing, pr, collaboration, ugc etc. Just like a random girl i started posting those filtered pictures on my ig idk tbhi cute lgti thi abhi cringe. But koe ni 16th years old pratiksha ko kch nhi pta tha tabhi. I used to create random lipsync reels etc tbhi tk koe bhi idea nhi tha what’s content creation bs main logon ke reels dekhti thi also tiktok was in trend tbhi toh. In 2022, i started doing affiliate marketing then mera thoda mind khula & i got to know about certain things, i bought my self owned phone Oneplus 9R in 2021 & i started vlogging & created my youtube channel becz i loved watching vlogs that time. I was focusing on youtube tbhi i didn’t have any idea about content creation on ig. Then Back in 2022, i joined my college & tbhi tk main thoda thoda mini vlog wale reels bnane lagi thi, i created more in college & it started going viral 200k, 300k, 10k, 1Million. OMG i never believed ki aisa bhi kch hoga kabhi becz my id was hacked once, kisi ne ek bar fake followers bdha die i removed that account ki reach was on 200-500 views, ye sb hone k bad bhi reels viral hona was a omg moment to me. So, i started working more on reels then My Manali Reel had gone viral upto 7 M, got very good response. But itte reels viral hone k bad bhi when i pitched to brands i didn’t get any collab becz my content was not aligning with their requirements. Then i started making contents related to lifestyle niche & again started pitching and you know what the good part is it worked !! I started getting collaborations. My First PR was of @wowskinscienceindia 🥹 
Then i started working more on my contents by making content calendars doing market research attending workshops i tried & tried to do different things.
Slowly & Steadily  i collaborated with 100+ big brands after June 2024. 
*Safar Khoobsurat Hai Manzil Se Bhi*
Consitency & Self Believe Matters 🦋✨
Karm|| Sabr|| Moksh🧿
